{
  "texts": [
    "He and Im [IL08, Theorem 1.4] gave an affirmative answer to this conjecture under the assumptions that K is of characteristic different from two and e = 1.",
    "Im with collaborators [BI08, IL13b, CI25] has obtained other results concerning Larsen's conjecture.",
    "See also the survey [IL21] by Im and Larsen.",
    "Geyer and Jarden [GJ78] conjectured that Statements (a)-(c) in (3) in this theorem hold for any finitely generated field K over its prime field.",
    "We note that the paper of Jacobson and Jarden [JJ84] involves a proof of Statement (a) for K with positive characteristic, but it contains an error as indicated in [JJ85]."
  ]
}